15) Final Locked Summary
	•	PaymentAttempt is the authoritative payment record and maps to Orders
	•	Wompi integration uses server-side verification + webhooks to mark payments PAID
	•	Idempotency, signature verification, audit logs, and retries are required
	•	Admin can record offline payments and refunds; Wompi refunds optional if enabled
	•	Secrets stored securely; provider config tenant-scoped and Admin-only

